s: I’ve owned a Wiltshire self sharpening knife for over 20 years and it still works great. I wanted to get additional size knives for ease of use. The smaller knife is exactly as expected. The larger knife is smaller than expected. It works, but I wanted it to cut through a watermelon, and it is small for this task. I’ve gone back to my original knife which is like a bread knife for cutting watermelon. ... I bought this brand ...
